{
  "texts": [
    "Table 4 shows the main results.",
    "Our main findings are as follows: Importance of Graph Context.",
    "When the graph context is not encoded (w/o Graph Encoder), the LLM's generation quality significantly declines (Hit@1: 0.7275 → 0.5835).",
    "This suggests that merely describing relationships between nodes and edges in text is insufficient for LLMs to fully comprehend the graph context.",
    "Embedding the graph enables the LLM to capture the graph's context at a deeper level."
  ]
}